Chýbala si mi.

13
00:03:56,900 --> 00:03:57,200
In.

14
00:03:59,500 --> 00:04:01,120
Už ma nikdy neopusti.

15
00:04:02,920 --> 00:04:04,280
Sľúb mi to.

16
00:04:31,110 --> 00:04:33,750
Posledné dni často plačeš.

17
00:04:39,150 --> 00:04:40,750
Otec...

18
00:04:41,370 --> 00:04:41,910
Prastarý otec...

19
00:04:41,910 --> 00:04:43,730
Kedy zomrel?

20
00:04:45,350 --> 00:04:47,810
Zomrel už dávno.

21
00:04:47,810 --> 00:04:50,310
Už si ani nepamätám.

22
00:04:50,770 --> 00:04:52,570
Ale mama...

23
00:04:53,310 --> 00:04:54,650
Tvoja prastará mama...

24
00:04:54,650 --> 00:04:57,830
Tá zomrela pred desiatimi rokmi.

25
00:04:59,090 --> 00:05:00,290
Tak...

26
00:05:00,290 --> 00:05:01,970
S kým teraz žiješ?

27
00:05:01,970 --> 00:05:03,770
Pretože Alin…

28
00:05:03,770 --> 00:05:05,890
Môžeš ju volať mama.

29
00:05:06,170 --> 00:05:07,250
Áno.

30
00:05:09,870 --> 00:05:11,650
Môžeš ju tak oslovovať.

31
00:05:11,650 --> 00:05:16,390
Však chodíš s Dean-om.

32
00:05:20,630 --> 00:05:22,730
Mama tu už nie je.

33
00:05:23,550 --> 00:05:25,790
Takže žiješ sama?

34
00:05:27,890 --> 00:05:29,470
Áno.

35
00:05:29,470 --> 00:05:31,610
Ale vždy ma sem chodia pozrieť moje vnúčatá.

36
00:05:31,610 --> 00:05:33,550
Nie som vôbec osamelá.

37
00:05:34,490 --> 00:05:35,530
Ak...

38
00:05:36,530 --> 00:05:39,070
Ak by som sem chodil aj ja,

39
00:05:39,390 --> 00:05:40,830
nevadilo by ti to?

40
00:05:42,490 --> 00:05:43,830
Nie, nevadilo.

41
00:05:44,370 --> 00:05:45,470
Parm.

42
00:05:45,470 --> 00:05:48,790
Vždy si tu vítaný.

43
00:05:49,750 --> 00:05:52,270
Ak ti budem chýbať,
príď ma navštíviť.

44
00:05:55,370 --> 00:05:57,410
Budem s ním sem chodiť často.

45
00:05:57,410 --> 00:05:58,250
Dobre.

46
00:06:00,390 --> 00:06:02,570
Budeme sem chodiť často.

47
00:06:02,570 --> 00:06:03,470
Cez víkend...

48
00:06:03,470 --> 00:06:05,530
ho sem zoberiem na obed.

49
00:06:05,530 --> 00:06:07,450
Dobre?

50
00:06:07,450 --> 00:06:08,430
Áno.

51
00:06:40,830 --> 00:06:41,770
Dean.

52
00:06:41,770 --> 00:06:42,850
Poďme sa najesť.

53
00:06:42,850 --> 00:06:44,770
An toho veľa navarila.

54
00:06:45,610 --> 00:06:47,530
Poďme.

55
00:07:06,450 --> 00:07:07,650
Poriadne sa najedz.

56
00:07:07,650 --> 00:07:08,370
Áno.

57
00:07:08,410 --> 00:07:08,930
Ochutnaj to.

58
00:07:08,970 --> 00:07:11,250
Ahoj, stará mama.

59
00:07:14,970 --> 00:07:16,850
Posaďte sa.

60
00:07:16,850 --> 00:07:19,310
Čo tu robí Parm?

61
00:07:20,310 --> 00:07:23,390
Videl som iba Dean-ove auto,
tak som si myslel, že prišiel sám.

62
00:07:24,230 --> 00:07:24,870
Takže...

63
00:07:24,870 --> 00:07:26,110
Dnes...

64
00:07:26,110 --> 00:07:28,510
Dnes si babke prišiel
predstaviť svojho priateľa?

65
00:07:31,770 --> 00:07:33,830
Včera Dean prespal u Parm-a!

66
00:07:33,830 --> 00:07:37,370
Nevedela som,
že ti ho príde tak skoro predstaviť.

67
00:07:37,370 --> 00:07:38,110
Dean.

68
00:07:38,110 --> 00:07:40,370
Prečo Parm-a otravuješ?

69
00:07:43,910 --> 00:07:46,630
Nič som neurobil, babka.

70
00:07:46,630 --> 00:07:48,430
Áno, nič neurobil.

71
00:07:48,430 --> 00:07:52,250
Takže sa chopil svojej šance Parm?

72
00:07:52,250 --> 00:07:53,270
Nie!

73
00:07:53,270 --> 00:07:54,810
Dean iba...

74
00:07:54,810 --> 00:07:56,430
Iba čo?

75
00:07:58,730 --> 00:08:00,350
Asi odpadnem.

76
00:08:00,350 --> 00:08:02,390
Prečo ich podpichujete?

77
00:08:02,390 --> 00:08:04,170
Nič sa nestalo, stará mama.

78
00:08:04,170 --> 00:08:06,250
Nič mi neurobil.

79
00:08:06,250 --> 00:08:08,600
O čom ste s babkou hovorili?

80
00:08:08,700 --> 00:08:11,250
Ako je možné,
že nemá proti vášmu vzťahu žiadne námietky?

81
00:08:12,250 --> 00:08:14,230
Nič som neurobil.

82
00:08:15,490 --> 00:08:19,130
Je roztomilý.
Prečo by som ich vzťah neakceptovala?

83
00:08:19,690 --> 00:08:21,830
Váš brat...

84
00:08:21,830 --> 00:08:25,650
O svojom priateľovi mi povedal
hneď v prvý deň nášho stretnutia.

85
00:08:26,010 --> 00:08:28,050
Je to skutočný muž.

86
00:08:28,050 --> 00:08:28,850
Už viem.

87
00:08:28,850 --> 00:08:32,730
Chceš si získať srdce starej mamy, predtým,
ako sa vrátia rodičia, však?

88
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:33,600
Huh?

89
00:08:34,669 --> 00:08:36,209
Ty zloduch.

90
00:08:37,289 --> 00:08:41,909
A čo váš výlet do Kanchanaburi?

91
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:44,290
Máš nejaký tajný plán?

92
00:08:44,290 --> 00:08:47,890
Mal by si sa priznať.

93
00:08:53,090 --> 00:08:54,630
Chcem...

94
00:08:54,630 --> 00:08:56,550
Chcem, aby ma odmenil.

95
00:08:56,870 --> 00:08:59,590
Za tú medailu z plaveckej súťaže.

96
00:08:59,750 --> 00:09:01,530
Preto ho beriem na ten výlet so sebou.

97
00:09:03,650 --> 00:09:05,270
Kvôli tebe sa teraz červená.

98
00:09:05,270 --> 00:09:06,790
Už dosť.

99
00:09:06,790 --> 00:09:08,290
Choďte pre ďalšie taniere.

100
00:09:08,290 --> 00:09:09,790
Idem pre ne.

101
00:09:09,790 --> 00:09:11,190
Aj poháre.

102
00:09:11,190 --> 00:09:13,230
Mal by si jej pomôcť.

103
00:09:13,470 --> 00:09:15,190
Už pre ne šla.

104
00:09:16,010 --> 00:09:17,090
Daj si ešte.

105
00:09:17,090 --> 00:09:19,050
Dnes vyzeráš šťastne.

106
00:09:22,650 --> 00:09:23,650
Áno.

107
00:09:31,260 --> 00:09:32,190
Ste roztomilí.

108
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:34,860
Tu je ryža.

109
00:09:46,900 --> 00:09:47,600
Pre teba, stará mama.

110
00:09:49,880 --> 00:09:51,540
Ochutnaj to.
Je to dobré?

111
00:09:51,940 --> 00:09:53,540
Uvarila som to sama.

112
00:09:55,760 --> 00:09:56,760
Chutí?

113
00:09:56,760 --> 00:09:58,000
Výborné.

